(stream-ref pythagorean-triples 1)  ; (6 8 10)
(stream-ref pythagorean-triples 2)  ; (5 12 13)
(stream-ref pythagorean-triples 3)  ; (9 12 15)
(stream-ref pythagorean-triples 4)  ; (8 15 17)
